1
00:00:55,000 --> 00:00:59,175
The Story of Minglan

2
00:00:59,175 --> 00:01:01,675
Episode 39

3
00:01:04,960 --> 00:01:06,920
Are you not afraid that

4
00:01:06,920 --> 00:01:08,680
I'll endure Cao Jinxiu and agree to that marriage?

5
00:01:14,520 --> 00:01:15,125
I'm not a person

6
00:01:15,125 --> 00:01:16,800
who is okay with anything.

7
00:01:17,460 --> 00:01:19,200
The same goes for you.

8
00:01:19,480 --> 00:01:21,440
Although you look obedient

9
00:01:21,440 --> 00:01:22,520
and can adapt easily,

10
00:01:22,760 --> 00:01:24,400
you are actually very stubborn.

11
00:01:25,320 --> 00:01:26,320
Hence,

12
00:01:26,800 --> 00:01:28,840
I used Cao family

13
00:01:28,840 --> 00:01:30,680
because I'm far away on the borders

14
00:01:30,680 --> 00:01:31,840
and can't empty my hands to handle it.

15
00:01:34,480 --> 00:01:36,040
It's enough to just delay you for a while.

16
00:01:36,520 --> 00:01:37,850
Moreover, even if your family agrees to

17
00:01:37,850 --> 00:01:38,640
accept such a proposal,

18
00:01:38,640 --> 00:01:40,080
I still have my ways.

19
00:01:40,110 --> 00:01:41,400
Stop bragging.

20
00:01:42,120 --> 00:01:43,760
without Wen Yanjing,

21
00:01:44,040 --> 00:01:45,320
would you have made it?

22
00:01:46,560 --> 00:01:48,600
I'm determined to have you.

23
00:01:48,640 --> 00:01:49,920
The heavens pitied me

24
00:01:49,920 --> 00:01:52,040
and sent Wen Yanjing to help me.

25
00:01:52,520 --> 00:01:55,080
That is because the heavens hate evil people!

26
00:01:57,880 --> 00:01:59,080
Well, whatever you say.

27
00:02:00,600 --> 00:02:02,880
Also, when I knew that your elder sister

28
00:02:02,880 --> 00:02:04,520
was dating Wen Yanjing secretly,

29
00:02:04,520 --> 00:02:05,520
I was so happy that

30
00:02:05,520 --> 00:02:07,240
I wasn't able to fall asleep again all night!

31
00:02:11,080 --> 00:02:12,080
Really.

32
00:02:12,640 --> 00:02:13,440
I feel that

33
00:02:13,560 --> 00:02:14,760
I've never exerted so much

34
00:02:14,760 --> 00:02:15,920
thought even in wars compared to this.

35
00:02:15,920 --> 00:02:16,900
This is called making a sound

36
00:02:16,900 --> 00:02:18,040
in the east to attack the west.

37
00:02:18,300 --> 00:02:19,800
I Just want to marry a wife,

38
00:02:19,800 --> 00:02:22,320
I've even used my knowledge in military tactics.

39
00:02:24,520 --> 00:02:25,320
You are talking about

40
00:02:25,320 --> 00:02:26,760
this matter too lightly.

41
00:02:26,960 --> 00:02:29,100
That was the reputation of my Fifth Sister,

42
00:02:29,160 --> 00:02:30,120
and the dignity of

43
00:02:30,120 --> 00:02:31,040
my whole Sheng Family.

44
00:02:33,240 --> 00:02:34,280
What if something bad happens,

45
00:02:34,280 --> 00:02:35,400
it would all be over!

46
00:02:36,760 --> 00:02:37,520
That's why

47
00:02:38,480 --> 00:02:39,560
I sent men to investigate the family background

48
00:02:39,560 --> 00:02:41,520
and character of Wen Yanjing.

49
00:02:42,440 --> 00:02:43,840
If he had a bad reputation,

50
00:02:44,440 --> 00:02:46,320
since he could be your future brother-in-law

51
00:02:46,320 --> 00:02:47,440
which is also mine.

52
00:02:47,840 --> 00:02:48,560
I would then hire some people

53
00:02:48,560 --> 00:02:50,280
to expel him out of the capital,

54
00:02:51,080 --> 00:02:52,680
so that he won't mess up your Sheng Family

55
00:02:52,680 --> 00:02:54,240
and destroy your reputation!

56
00:02:54,840 --> 00:02:55,760
You...

57
00:02:59,480 --> 00:03:00,760
You cast such a huge net.

58
00:03:03,880 --> 00:03:05,240
Not only that.

59
00:03:05,880 --> 00:03:08,550
Your father and his wife,

60
00:03:08,560 --> 00:03:10,640
and your Sister Rulan's temper and personalities

61
00:03:10,880 --> 00:03:12,280
have already been clearly understood by me

62
00:03:12,280 --> 00:03:13,640
thanks to your Second Brother Changbai.

63
00:03:16,600 --> 00:03:17,440
Your father

64
00:03:17,800 --> 00:03:18,825
loves his clean reputation

65
00:03:18,825 --> 00:03:20,040
more than his wife and children.

66
00:03:20,600 --> 00:03:23,480
His wife is muddled and short-sighted.

67
00:03:23,680 --> 00:03:25,160
Your Sister Rulan

68
00:03:25,160 --> 00:03:27,680
is simple, infatuated, open, and candid.

69
00:03:28,480 --> 00:03:29,280
Also,

70
00:03:29,680 --> 00:03:30,925
I was sure that your Brother Changbai

71
00:03:30,960 --> 00:03:32,080
won't turn hostile against me

72
00:03:32,080 --> 00:03:33,080
even if he learns about this matter,

73
00:03:33,720 --> 00:03:35,960
so I boldly implemented it.

74
00:03:36,320 --> 00:03:37,080
Everything,

75
00:03:37,080 --> 00:03:38,075
even if the timing, place, and people

76
00:03:38,075 --> 00:03:38,760
are all perfect,

77
00:03:38,760 --> 00:03:40,960
it won't work even without luck.

78
00:03:44,930 --> 00:03:46,360
I'm not done talking yet!

79
00:03:46,680 --> 00:03:48,280
What do you treat me as?

80
00:03:49,120 --> 00:03:50,520
A wild pig in a trap,

81
00:03:50,520 --> 00:03:51,800
or a herring in a fish net?

82
00:03:52,600 --> 00:03:54,080
Gu Tingye,

83
00:03:54,080 --> 00:03:56,080
you're a ruffian, a scoundrel!

84
00:04:14,280 --> 00:04:15,400
My Young Master,

85
00:04:15,440 --> 00:04:17,200
what did you say to Sixth Miss

86
00:04:17,200 --> 00:04:18,480
making her so shocked like that.

87
00:04:19,560 --> 00:04:21,000
Nothing.

88
00:04:21,680 --> 00:04:23,360
I just expressed my sincerity.

89
00:04:23,360 --> 00:04:24,200
But it seemed that

90
00:04:24,200 --> 00:04:25,640
it was not the case.

91
00:04:26,040 --> 00:04:26,840
Haven't you always said that

92
00:04:26,840 --> 00:04:28,680
you will be very kind to her

93
00:04:28,920 --> 00:04:30,110
How come that it didn't work today?

94
00:04:30,120 --> 00:04:31,440
It didn't work?

95
00:04:31,850 --> 00:04:33,360
It worked so perfectly!

96
00:04:37,160 --> 00:04:38,975
The results of the civil examination

97
00:04:38,975 --> 00:04:39,760
will be announced today?

98
00:04:39,760 --> 00:04:40,960
Right.

99
00:04:43,620 --> 00:04:45,125
Have some rest.

100
00:04:45,240 --> 00:04:46,560
We might need to

101
00:04:46,560 --> 00:04:48,280
meet another person today.

102
00:04:57,720 --> 00:04:58,800
Gu Tingye...

103
00:05:00,440 --> 00:05:02,080
How is this possible?

104
00:05:02,080 --> 00:05:03,480
It's true.

105
00:05:03,640 --> 00:05:04,840
That Old Madam Sheng

106
00:05:04,840 --> 00:05:05,920
also said the same thing.

107
00:05:06,020 --> 00:05:07,040
Absolutely impossible!

108
00:05:08,120 --> 00:05:08,800
Even if the Sheng Family

109
00:05:08,800 --> 00:05:09,680
will marry off a daughter,

110
00:05:10,000 --> 00:05:11,480
it would be Rulan!

111
00:05:11,930 --> 00:05:13,160
That Big Madam Wang

112
00:05:13,160 --> 00:05:14,520
won't allow an illegitimate daughter

113
00:05:14,520 --> 00:05:15,920
to marry off into an marquis' house.

114
00:05:16,000 --> 00:05:17,240
That Rulan has already been set to marry a scholar

115
00:05:17,240 --> 00:05:19,360
who passed the Imperial examination.

116
00:05:19,360 --> 00:05:21,040
He's a scholar promoted by the Sheng Family.

117
00:05:21,800 --> 00:05:22,680
Gu Tingye

118
00:05:23,480 --> 00:05:25,200
was a little bit late in proposing marriage,

119
00:05:25,520 --> 00:05:27,280
so he settled with Minglan.

120
00:05:30,680 --> 00:05:33,840
Son, this is fate.

121
00:05:34,040 --> 00:05:35,400
He was late,

122
00:05:35,400 --> 00:05:36,960
so were you.

123
00:05:37,650 --> 00:05:39,400
Stop putting too much fuss on it.

124
00:05:40,880 --> 00:05:43,040
Forget Minglan.

125
00:05:44,640 --> 00:05:45,400
No.

126
00:05:47,280 --> 00:05:48,280
This is not right.

127
00:05:49,280 --> 00:05:50,960
This is totally wrong.

128
00:05:51,630 --> 00:05:52,600
Yuanruo!

129
00:05:53,440 --> 00:05:54,600
Yuanruo!

130
00:05:56,160 --> 00:05:58,880
Don't go to the Sheng Manor and cause ruckus!

131
00:06:13,720 --> 00:06:14,600
Yuanruo.

132
00:06:17,720 --> 00:06:19,160
Second Uncle, you came so late.

133
00:06:19,760 --> 00:06:20,920
You are really busy.

134
00:06:24,880 --> 00:06:26,200
I heard you passed the civil examination.

135
00:06:26,200 --> 00:06:27,440
This is something worth celebrating.

136
00:06:28,080 --> 00:06:29,360
Congratulations.

137
00:06:30,720 --> 00:06:31,550
Emmm...

138
00:06:32,560 --> 00:06:34,520
Why are you unhappy?

139
00:06:34,520 --> 00:06:35,880
Who angered you?

140
00:06:36,170 --> 00:06:37,000
You clearly know that

141
00:06:37,000 --> 00:06:38,690
I love Minglan.

142
00:06:38,720 --> 00:06:40,640
Why did you still promise the Sheng Family that

143
00:06:40,640 --> 00:06:42,200
you're going to marry her? What is your intention?

144
00:06:45,200 --> 00:06:46,880
You're still thinking about her?

145
00:06:47,920 --> 00:06:49,560
I didn't know that.

146
00:06:49,920 --> 00:06:51,040
I only know that

147
00:06:51,040 --> 00:06:52,075
after you lost your wife,

148
00:06:52,075 --> 00:06:54,000
you shut yourself up and focused on your studies.

149
00:06:54,160 --> 00:06:54,900
You didn't inquire about

150
00:06:54,900 --> 00:06:55,840
the matters happening outside.

151
00:06:56,960 --> 00:06:59,120
I thought that you'd let it go.

152
00:06:59,840 --> 00:07:01,560
You can't blame me for this

153
00:07:01,560 --> 00:07:03,080
It is a strange combination of circumstances, right?

154
00:07:03,960 --> 00:07:05,120
I heard of it.

155
00:07:05,720 --> 00:07:06,480
The one you're supposed to marry

156
00:07:06,480 --> 00:07:07,750
is the legitimate daughter of the Sheng Family.

157
00:07:07,840 --> 00:07:09,120
But she was already set to marry someone else,

158
00:07:09,120 --> 00:07:10,520
so you chose Minglan instead.

159
00:07:11,280 --> 00:07:12,040
In your eyes,

160
00:07:12,040 --> 00:07:13,720
she was just a substitute.

161
00:07:14,120 --> 00:07:15,280
Let her go.

162
00:07:15,880 --> 00:07:18,320
You were the first one to give her up.

163
00:07:20,440 --> 00:07:22,240
I urged you back then

164
00:07:23,320 --> 00:07:25,680
to not fear the power of Prince Yong.

165
00:07:25,960 --> 00:07:27,480
If you had agreed,

166
00:07:27,520 --> 00:07:28,360
I would have risked

167
00:07:28,360 --> 00:07:30,200
my life to make you two

168
00:07:30,800 --> 00:07:32,200
be together.

169
00:07:32,560 --> 00:07:33,720
But what did you do?

170
00:07:34,000 --> 00:07:34,960
You were being such a coward

171
00:07:34,960 --> 00:07:36,640
and didn't dare to take the risk.

172
00:07:36,760 --> 00:07:38,200
You gave her up,

173
00:07:38,200 --> 00:07:40,020
so why are you blaming me now?

174
00:07:40,040 --> 00:07:41,880
I didn't give her up!

175
00:07:42,680 --> 00:07:44,025
I must pass the Imperial examination first

176
00:07:44,025 --> 00:07:44,520
to get a high rank

177
00:07:44,680 --> 00:07:45,450
so I could have the diginity

178
00:07:45,450 --> 00:07:46,680
to propose marriage to the Sheng Family.

179
00:07:46,790 --> 00:07:48,400
However, I was late.

180
00:07:49,490 --> 00:07:51,200
You want your dignity?

181
00:07:51,720 --> 00:07:53,520
Does the Sixth Miss not need hers too?

182
00:07:55,480 --> 00:07:57,000
Your matter with Minglan back then

183
00:07:57,000 --> 00:07:58,040
was discussed widely throughout the capital.

184
00:07:58,240 --> 00:07:59,560
Everyone here in the capital

185
00:07:59,560 --> 00:08:00,840
knew it.

186
00:08:01,400 --> 00:08:02,680
You could indeed not marry her

187
00:08:02,680 --> 00:08:03,783
and marry a princess of the second rank.

188
00:08:04,325 --> 00:08:06,400
No one would talk against you.

189
00:08:06,400 --> 00:08:08,440
But what happened to Minglan

190
00:08:08,440 --> 00:08:09,175
who is just an illegitimate daughter

191
00:08:09,175 --> 00:08:09,760
of a lower-ranking official?

192
00:08:10,320 --> 00:08:11,560
Didn't you know?

193
00:08:12,760 --> 00:08:13,880
Moreover,

194
00:08:14,320 --> 00:08:15,760
if you really wanted to marry Minglan,

195
00:08:16,120 --> 00:08:17,280
if you had proposed marriage to

196
00:08:17,280 --> 00:08:18,125
the Sheng Family immediately

197
00:08:18,125 --> 00:08:18,840
after your wife's death,

198
00:08:18,840 --> 00:08:20,320
you would have a chance.

199
00:08:20,600 --> 00:08:22,240
But you didn't go.

200
00:08:22,330 --> 00:08:23,225
You said that you had to wait

201
00:08:23,225 --> 00:08:24,120
to pass the civil examination.

202
00:08:24,840 --> 00:08:26,480
If you didn't pass this year,

203
00:08:26,880 --> 00:08:27,750
you were going to make her wait

204
00:08:27,750 --> 00:08:28,320
for three more years?

205
00:08:28,320 --> 00:08:29,600
Six more years?

206
00:08:30,000 --> 00:08:31,200
Forever waiting like that,

207
00:08:31,200 --> 00:08:32,440
waiting for you to have prestige

208
00:08:32,440 --> 00:08:33,440
before you go to her family for proposal?

209
00:08:35,400 --> 00:08:37,480
I didn't do it just to have prestige.

210
00:08:38,600 --> 00:08:39,575
Last time,

211
00:08:39,575 --> 00:08:41,920
when our situation hadn't been finalized yet,

212
00:08:42,760 --> 00:08:44,000
I had rushed to make her a promise.

213
00:08:45,280 --> 00:08:46,680
In the end, I just broke my oath

214
00:08:47,280 --> 00:08:48,600
and broke her heart.

215
00:08:48,960 --> 00:08:50,160
So this time,

216
00:08:50,160 --> 00:08:51,520
I must be 100% sure

217
00:08:51,880 --> 00:08:53,200
before I go before her family to propose.

218
00:08:53,800 --> 00:08:56,200
I...am also not blaming you.

219
00:08:57,080 --> 00:08:57,880
I'm just saying that

220
00:08:58,920 --> 00:08:59,950
if you had your predicament

221
00:08:59,950 --> 00:09:01,200
and were thus unable to marry her,

222
00:09:01,730 --> 00:09:03,050
then you shouldn't blame a late-comer like me

223
00:09:03,050 --> 00:09:03,840
for surpassing you.

224
00:09:06,840 --> 00:09:08,050
You are not taking no one but her

225
00:09:08,050 --> 00:09:08,600
as your wife, right?

226
00:09:09,360 --> 00:09:11,080
How do you know that I'm not?

227
00:09:23,800 --> 00:09:25,640
So you have had an affection on her from early on.

228
00:09:28,560 --> 00:09:30,640
Yuanruo, since our discussion

229
00:09:30,640 --> 00:09:32,000
has reached this point,

230
00:09:32,440 --> 00:09:33,760
I'll be honest with you.

231
00:09:35,200 --> 00:09:36,120
In the past,

232
00:09:36,640 --> 00:09:38,440
I saw you two having mutual affection

233
00:09:38,440 --> 00:09:39,560
and loathing to part from each other.

234
00:09:40,400 --> 00:09:42,040
I really wanted to support you two.

235
00:09:43,320 --> 00:09:44,160
But afterward,

236
00:09:44,160 --> 00:09:45,560
I saw you being unable to

237
00:09:45,560 --> 00:09:46,175
keep your relationship going

238
00:09:46,175 --> 00:09:46,680
and disappointing her,

239
00:09:46,800 --> 00:09:48,440
I then made up my mind

240
00:09:48,770 --> 00:09:50,640
that once I returned with honor,

241
00:09:50,850 --> 00:09:52,560
I surely will marry Minglan.

242
00:09:56,280 --> 00:09:58,480
How sure are you that

243
00:09:58,480 --> 00:10:00,120
she's willing to marry you?

244
00:10:02,080 --> 00:10:03,440
Just in order to marry her,

245
00:10:04,240 --> 00:10:05,920
I fought hard in the wars,

246
00:10:05,925 --> 00:10:07,550
charged into the front line, bled blood

247
00:10:07,550 --> 00:10:08,280
and risked my life,

248
00:10:08,380 --> 00:10:09,280
before I was able to

249
00:10:09,280 --> 00:10:10,670
obtain today's honor.

250
00:10:10,680 --> 00:10:11,760
If you can't accept it,

251
00:10:11,760 --> 00:10:13,120
you can go ask her,

252
00:10:13,160 --> 00:10:15,320
and ask the Old Madam in their house.

253
00:10:16,520 --> 00:10:17,560
Okay.

254
00:10:23,820 --> 00:10:24,525
Young Master,

255
00:10:24,880 --> 00:10:26,040
how could you let the Young Lord

256
00:10:26,040 --> 00:10:27,080
go and ask Sixth Miss?

257
00:10:27,680 --> 00:10:29,200
She had more affection on Young Lord

258
00:10:29,200 --> 00:10:31,480
than that on you.

259
00:10:37,910 --> 00:10:40,160
The will of Sixth Miss Sheng

260
00:10:40,160 --> 00:10:41,080
is very firm and clear.

261
00:10:42,160 --> 00:10:43,560
Before, I was indeed very afraid that

262
00:10:43,560 --> 00:10:44,960
she'd choose He Hongwen.

263
00:10:45,280 --> 00:10:46,200
But I know that

264
00:10:47,000 --> 00:10:48,120
no matter what happens,

265
00:10:48,760 --> 00:10:50,680
she won't choose Young Lord Qi again.

266
00:11:04,680 --> 00:11:06,560
Old Madam said that she's not feeling well.

267
00:11:06,560 --> 00:11:07,840
the Young Lord, please just go back.

268
00:11:10,400 --> 00:11:12,880
Then, I will come again next time.

269
00:11:12,880 --> 00:11:14,240
Don't bother.

270
00:11:15,200 --> 00:11:16,320
Why?

271
00:11:16,800 --> 00:11:18,320
Old Madam said that you came today surely

272
00:11:18,320 --> 00:11:20,080
to ask her to convince Sixth Miss.

273
00:11:20,360 --> 00:11:22,025
Sixth Miss listens to Old Madam the most.

274
00:11:22,025 --> 00:11:22,040
She surely will not disobey her grandmother.

275
00:11:22,055 --> 00:11:23,720
She surely will not disobey her grandmother.

276
00:11:29,200 --> 00:11:30,400
Old Madam

277
00:11:30,400 --> 00:11:31,690
really knows everything.

278
00:11:31,760 --> 00:11:33,000
Hence, Old Madam said that

279
00:11:33,280 --> 00:11:35,080
you shouldn't waste your effort.

280
00:11:35,280 --> 00:11:36,160
She still can remember

281
00:11:36,160 --> 00:11:37,080
what you've done before.

282
00:11:37,400 --> 00:11:38,250
Although the Sheng Family

283
00:11:38,250 --> 00:11:39,200
isn't an aristocratic family

284
00:11:39,200 --> 00:11:41,000
and Sixth Miss is just an illegitimate daughter,

285
00:11:41,000 --> 00:11:42,340
we have some backbone.

286
00:11:42,480 --> 00:11:43,450
We won't be rushing to someone

287
00:11:43,450 --> 00:11:44,240
at their beck and call.

