Although the gates of the Sheng Manor is small,

292
00:11:50,280 --> 00:11:52,040
we still put importance to our dignity.

293
00:12:10,680 --> 00:12:11,640
Miss Xiaotao,

294
00:12:13,360 --> 00:12:14,600
I beg you to let me in.

295
00:12:15,680 --> 00:12:17,040
