302
00:12:26,640 --> 00:12:27,880
No choice?

303
00:12:28,520 --> 00:12:29,520
The Sixth Miss repeatedly refused you,

304
00:12:29,520 --> 00:12:30,800
but you didn't give up.

305
00:12:30,820 --> 00:12:31,375
You clearly knew that

306
00:12:31,375 --> 00:12:32,400
