309
00:12:35,420 --> 00:12:36,880
No matter where she went after that,

310
00:12:36,880 --> 00:12:37,650
there were people laughing at Sixth Miss

311
00:12:37,650 --> 00:12:38,200
for having wishful thinking,

312
00:12:38,200 --> 00:12:38,840
do you know that?

313
00:12:41,040 --> 00:12:41,840
Forget it.

314
00:12:42,080 --> 00:12:43,000
The Sixth Miss will be married off soon.

315
00:12:43,000 --> 00:12:44,000
Just leave.

316
00:12:51,240 --> 00:12:52,320
She...

317
00:12:54,480 --> 00:12:56,160
