318
00:13:05,080 --> 00:13:06,240
I...

319
00:13:09,120 --> 00:13:10,680
I just want her to live a good life in the future.

320
00:13:10,680 --> 00:13:11,225
It's none of your business

321
00:13:11,225 --> 00:13:12,840
