322
00:13:12,840 --> 00:13:14,160
you broke your promise anyway!

323
00:13:14,160 --> 00:13:14,920
And you still have the nerve to ask,

324
00:13:14,920 --> 00:13:15,960
if she's living well?

325
00:13:17,800 --> 00:13:18,760
If you still don't leave...

326
00:14:22,600 --> 00:14:24,040
Actually,

327
00:14:24,920 --> 00:14:27,040
