328
00:14:28,560 --> 00:14:29,920
Anyway,

329
00:14:29,920 --> 00:14:30,775
Old Madam still hasn't agreed

330
00:14:30,775 --> 00:14:31,800
with the proposal of the Gu Family.

331
00:14:32,400 --> 00:14:33,440
How about...

332
00:14:40,920 --> 00:14:42,360
Danju,

333
00:14:43,560 --> 00:14:45,280
never look back.

334
00:15:10,080 --> 00:15:12,960
Second Brother, you're getting married?

335
00:15:16,240 --> 00:15:17,760
It's a miss from the Sheng family.

336
00:15:18,880 --> 00:15:20,920
This is a granted marriage by His Majesty.

337
00:15:21,160 --> 00:15:23,840
Big Madam, stop secretly discussing my marriage

338
00:15:23,840 --> 00:15:25,600
with other families.

339
00:15:26,120 --> 00:15:28,160
This matter is already finalized.

340
00:15:28,200 --> 00:15:29,720
No one can break it up!

341
00:15:31,760 --> 00:15:33,080
How could I?

342
00:15:34,120 --> 00:15:35,960
This is a

343
00:15:35,960 --> 00:15:37,280
grand Imperial grace,

344
00:15:37,490 --> 00:15:39,320
of course, I'm so happy.

345
00:15:40,680 --> 00:15:42,440
When do you plan to do it,

346
00:15:42,520 --> 00:15:43,600
so I

347
00:15:43,600 --> 00:15:45,280
can start preparing.

348
00:15:45,960 --> 00:15:47,640
We have few sevants in our manor.

349
00:15:47,640 --> 00:15:49,500
we need to hire outsiders

350
00:15:49,560 --> 00:15:51,680
to help us with the chores.

351
00:15:53,080 --> 00:15:54,760
No need to trouble you for that, Big Madam.

352
00:15:55,480 --> 00:15:56,920
My marriage

353
00:15:56,920 --> 00:15:58,200
will be organized

354
00:15:58,200 --> 00:15:59,200
by people from the palace.

355
00:15:59,480 --> 00:16:00,760
Prince Huan is a close friend of mine.

356
00:16:01,240 --> 00:16:02,880
He surely will send some people to help out.

357
00:16:03,560 --> 00:16:04,840
By then,

358
00:16:05,160 --> 00:16:07,200
Big Madam and Eldest Brother

359
00:16:07,320 --> 00:16:08,920
just need to sit there, drink some wine,

360
00:16:08,920 --> 00:16:09,760
and accept the bows of other people.

361
00:16:12,720 --> 00:16:13,600
That's fine.

362
00:16:14,760 --> 00:16:15,960
That's fine.

363
00:16:17,560 --> 00:16:19,160
It's an Imperial grace after all.

364
00:16:20,960 --> 00:16:22,440
Since

365
00:16:23,040 --> 00:16:24,920
Big Madam doesn't have any objections,

366
00:16:25,760 --> 00:16:27,480
there shouldn't be any problem

367
00:16:27,480 --> 00:16:28,950
with Eldest Brother and Sister-in-law either,

368
00:16:30,680 --> 00:16:32,480
You clearly

369
00:16:32,480 --> 00:16:34,240
have made up your mind,

370
00:16:35,080 --> 00:16:36,800
no need to ask us.

371
00:16:39,240 --> 00:16:40,640
Pretentious display of

372
00:16:40,640 --> 00:16:42,040
proper etiquette should still be done.

373
00:16:42,920 --> 00:16:45,320
Or else, if this great talent of

374
00:16:45,320 --> 00:16:47,040
our Gu Family got lost because of me,

375
00:16:47,740 --> 00:16:49,280
won't it be too bad?

376
00:16:53,480 --> 00:16:54,480
Okay.

377
00:16:55,200 --> 00:16:56,760
I'll just go looking around the house.

378
00:16:57,240 --> 00:16:58,160
I'll check if there are areas

379
00:16:58,160 --> 00:16:59,240
that should be renovated

380
00:16:59,240 --> 00:17:00,840
and let them record it.

381
00:17:01,000 --> 00:17:02,640
We'll start the construction tomorrow.

382
00:17:02,640 --> 00:17:04,240
You're going to have the house renovated?

383
00:17:06,240 --> 00:17:07,320
Don't worry.

384
00:17:07,360 --> 00:17:09,200
I won't use any money of the marquis' house.

385
00:17:10,720 --> 00:17:12,320
I just feel that

386
00:17:13,400 --> 00:17:16,920
aren't you making this

387
00:17:17,120 --> 00:17:18,200
much too grand?

388
00:17:20,240 --> 00:17:21,160
Even when your father got married

389
00:17:21,160 --> 00:17:23,000
in his first marriage,

390
00:17:23,440 --> 00:17:25,920
he didn't mobilize so many people to organize it.

391
00:17:27,170 --> 00:17:29,280
I fear that you might end up with

392
00:17:29,640 --> 00:17:32,040
a reputation of going beyond the usual.

393
00:17:35,080 --> 00:17:36,440
Making it this grand

394
00:17:36,440 --> 00:17:37,880
is His Majesty's intention.

395
00:17:38,480 --> 00:17:39,960
He felt that I'm a meritorious general,

396
00:17:39,960 --> 00:17:41,160
so I should be rewarded.

397
00:17:41,430 --> 00:17:43,600
But I'm a military official.

398
00:17:43,600 --> 00:17:45,400
I can't be conferred a much higher official rank.

399
00:17:45,480 --> 00:17:46,725
He can only reward me more

400
00:17:46,725 --> 00:17:47,960
in terms of money and items.

401
00:17:48,640 --> 00:17:49,640
At that time,

402
00:17:49,640 --> 00:17:51,080
Prince Huan will surely come.

403
00:17:51,200 --> 00:17:52,600
Perhaps even the Empress

404
00:17:52,600 --> 00:17:53,920
will come to attend the wedding too.

405
00:17:54,480 --> 00:17:55,880
If I don't do some renovations,

406
00:17:56,760 --> 00:17:58,000
it seems unreasonable.

407
00:18:04,440 --> 00:18:05,480
I'll take off then.

408
00:18:16,680 --> 00:18:18,520
What does your second brother mean by that?

409
00:18:19,200 --> 00:18:20,200
How could the Emperor allow him

410
00:18:20,200 --> 00:18:21,840
to have a wedding that's beyond the norms?

411
00:18:22,920 --> 00:18:25,640
He must be eyeing your noble title

412
00:18:26,480 --> 00:18:28,160
and is trying to test you.

413
00:18:29,960 --> 00:18:32,040
I really have no strength to think

414
00:18:32,610 --> 00:18:33,880
or care about it.

415
00:18:35,280 --> 00:18:36,920
Just let him torment himself if he wants.

416
00:18:41,160 --> 00:18:42,400
I'm tired.

417
00:18:48,800 --> 00:18:50,320
I'll take off now.

418
00:19:00,760 --> 00:19:01,240
Later,

419
00:19:01,240 --> 00:19:02,440
you also go there to measure.

420
00:19:02,840 --> 00:19:03,200
Measure that area.

421
00:19:03,200 --> 00:19:04,200
Come, let me see.

422
00:19:04,720 --> 00:19:06,480
Make it tidier! Hang up that lantern!

423
00:19:06,760 --> 00:19:07,520
This one...

424
00:19:11,040 --> 00:19:11,840
Did you jot it all down?

425
00:19:11,840 --> 00:19:13,080
We did! We did! Young Lord.

426
00:19:14,470 --> 00:19:16,200
Was what Big Madam said true?

427
00:19:17,320 --> 00:19:17,925
Second Brother plans

428
00:19:17,925 --> 00:19:18,800
