429
00:19:20,570 --> 00:19:22,560
The two of us have no sons.

430
00:19:23,520 --> 00:19:25,200
My noble title

431
00:19:25,960 --> 00:19:28,040
will be his once I die, so why would he

432
00:19:28,040 --> 00:19:29,480
want to take it away now?

433
00:19:30,640 --> 00:19:31,800
The person who really wants to

434
00:19:31,800 --> 00:19:32,720
steal my noble title away

435
00:19:32,920 --> 00:19:34,800
is Big Madam!

436
00:19:36,280 --> 00:19:37,920
She probably have been wishing for

437
00:19:37,920 --> 00:19:39,840
my death since long ago.

438
00:19:40,400 --> 00:19:42,440
While Old Second wasn't around,

439
00:19:42,640 --> 00:19:44,050
she would have let her Third Son

440
00:19:44,050 --> 00:19:44,840
inherit the title.

441
00:19:47,000 --> 00:19:48,880
But isn't Second Brother back?

442
00:19:51,360 --> 00:19:53,000
So what?

443
00:19:54,200 --> 00:19:54,850
The jar got broken

444
00:19:54,850 --> 00:19:56,400
while it still hasn't been taken way from the well yet.

445
00:19:57,000 --> 00:19:59,520
A general can die on the battlefield.

446
00:20:01,600 --> 00:20:02,675
When Second Brother goes out

447
00:20:02,675 --> 00:20:03,880
for expeditions in the future,

448
00:20:04,120 --> 00:20:06,440
we can't be sure of his life.

449
00:20:07,320 --> 00:20:09,960
If I still don't have any descendants soon,

450
00:20:12,520 --> 00:20:14,280
it will then be very beneficial to that Big Madam

451
00:20:14,280 --> 00:20:15,760
who is also my maternal aunt.

452
00:20:17,600 --> 00:20:19,320
Just wait and see.

453
00:20:20,440 --> 00:20:21,700
That Miss of the Sheng Family

454
00:20:21,700 --> 00:20:23,000
who is marrying into our family

455
00:20:24,160 --> 00:20:25,600
will suffer soon.

456
00:20:32,600 --> 00:20:34,480
Later, you tell them

457
00:20:34,760 --> 00:20:36,120
to hang them over there too.

458
00:20:36,120 --> 00:20:36,600
Ok.

459
00:20:36,600 --> 00:20:38,200
I want to hang some

460
00:20:38,200 --> 00:20:38,960
huge lanterns over there.

461
00:20:39,040 --> 00:20:40,560
Right. Right. Huge lanterns,

462
00:20:40,560 --> 00:20:41,520
the red ones.

463
00:20:41,600 --> 00:20:42,625
That Gu Tingye

464
00:20:42,640 --> 00:20:44,000
is a monstrous spider!

465
00:20:44,000 --> 00:20:45,730
He wove such a huge web!

466
00:20:45,760 --> 00:20:46,600
He wanted me to have now way out

467
00:20:46,600 --> 00:20:47,920
and just submit to his will.

468
00:20:48,200 --> 00:20:49,000
When have I ever encountered

469
00:20:49,000 --> 00:20:49,880
such a thing?

470
00:20:50,400 --> 00:20:52,080
I was so scared that I rushed back home.

471
00:20:52,600 --> 00:20:54,320
He really arranged it

472
00:20:55,320 --> 00:20:57,040
so accurately and ruthlessly.

473
00:20:58,680 --> 00:21:00,320
It's not that ruthless.

474
00:21:00,800 --> 00:21:03,240
Although he's a bit ferocious,

475
00:21:03,240 --> 00:21:04,640
his natural temperament is good.

476
00:21:05,600 --> 00:21:07,040
At the Youyang River,

477
00:21:07,040 --> 00:21:08,520
when the rebels caused trouble,

478
00:21:08,520 --> 00:21:09,480
and during the palace siege,

479
00:21:09,920 --> 00:21:10,840
that Gu Tingye

480
00:21:10,840 --> 00:21:12,480
did save my life.

481
00:21:13,280 --> 00:21:14,320
Afterwards,

482
00:21:14,320 --> 00:21:16,280
he even considered my reputation

483
00:21:16,280 --> 00:21:18,560
and didn't publicize it or ask for any reward.

484
00:21:19,240 --> 00:21:20,960
He can be considered to be an upright gentleman.

485
00:21:22,720 --> 00:21:24,400
So many things happened?

486
00:21:24,960 --> 00:21:26,520
You never told them to me!

487
00:21:28,000 --> 00:21:29,120
Those...

488
00:21:29,480 --> 00:21:31,240
those successive incidents...

489
00:21:31,830 --> 00:21:34,680
I-I...was afraid that you would scold me.

490
00:21:34,920 --> 00:21:36,120
I didn't dare to tell you.

491
00:21:40,400 --> 00:21:42,360
It's also not your fault.

492
00:21:43,180 --> 00:21:44,560
That man

493
00:21:45,240 --> 00:21:47,080
was too scheming.

494
00:21:52,120 --> 00:21:53,320
Let me ask you,

495
00:21:54,160 --> 00:21:55,480
when Gu Tingye

496
00:21:55,920 --> 00:21:58,080
told everything to you,

497
00:21:59,200 --> 00:22:00,480
what were you thinking?

498
00:22:06,840 --> 00:22:08,400
At the beginning,

499
00:22:08,400 --> 00:22:10,760
I was a bit happy.

500
00:22:11,560 --> 00:22:13,280
There was actually someone

501
00:22:13,280 --> 00:22:14,480
who exerted so much efforts to get me.

502
00:22:15,800 --> 00:22:18,640
Afterwards, I felt...

503
00:22:20,000 --> 00:22:21,360
I got mad as I thought more about it.

504
00:22:21,360 --> 00:22:23,040
I so wanted to slap him in the face!

505
00:22:25,040 --> 00:22:26,920
Then afterwards,

506
00:22:26,920 --> 00:22:28,560
I got anxious.

507
00:22:28,960 --> 00:22:30,040
Grandmother,

508
00:22:30,040 --> 00:22:31,160
say， this person is too good.

509
00:22:31,180 --> 00:22:32,760
What should I do in the future?

510
00:22:35,240 --> 00:22:37,280
The trap is too huge.

511
00:22:37,680 --> 00:22:39,075
If it is not because we are being forced

512
00:22:39,075 --> 00:22:40,240
by the current circumstances

513
00:22:40,680 --> 00:22:42,400
with him swindling us like that,

514
00:22:42,800 --> 00:22:44,360
