515
00:22:45,560 --> 00:22:46,100
As they say,

516
00:22:46,100 --> 00:22:48,000
serving the Emperor is like being with a tiger.

517
00:22:48,240 --> 00:22:49,320
He racked his brains like that

518
00:22:49,320 --> 00:22:51,160
just to marry me,

519
00:22:51,440 --> 00:22:53,280
what if in the future he starts to spurn me,

520
00:22:53,440 --> 00:22:54,080
what will he then

521
00:22:54,080 --> 00:22:55,960
plan to do?

522
00:22:58,280 --> 00:22:59,320
Also...

523
00:23:00,940 --> 00:23:03,320
Also, he knows about everything that

524
00:23:03,320 --> 00:23:04,600
happened between Qi Heng and I.

525
00:23:04,600 --> 00:23:05,440
Won't that mean

526
00:23:05,450 --> 00:23:06,400
my weakness is

527
00:23:06,400 --> 00:23:07,800
in his hands?

528
00:23:09,640 --> 00:23:10,960
Their Gu Family matters

529
00:23:10,960 --> 00:23:12,280
are also so tangled up.

530
00:23:13,920 --> 00:23:17,280
I am afraid that I won't be able to handle it.

531
00:23:19,800 --> 00:23:21,440
As long as you're unwilling,

532
00:23:21,800 --> 00:23:23,680
even if it is a granted marriage by the Emperor,

533
00:23:24,120 --> 00:23:26,240
I won't hand you over.

534
00:23:38,160 --> 00:23:39,880
Even Old Madam

535
00:23:39,880 --> 00:23:41,560
has tried to convince her twice.

536
00:23:42,760 --> 00:23:44,360
Minglan

537
00:23:44,360 --> 00:23:46,560
just say no to it.

538
00:23:48,240 --> 00:23:50,040
I think this matter...

539
00:23:51,000 --> 00:23:52,640
will be a bit hard to push through.

540
00:23:53,560 --> 00:23:54,840
Wait a few more days.

541
00:23:59,120 --> 00:24:00,480
The Sixth Little Sister

542
00:24:00,480 --> 00:24:02,200
is not some usual ladies.

543
00:24:02,240 --> 00:24:03,800
I know her very well.

544
00:24:04,280 --> 00:24:05,635
Don't see her only as being gentle,

545
00:24:05,640 --> 00:24:06,880
submissive, modest,

546
00:24:06,880 --> 00:24:08,120
and very filial,

547
00:24:08,640 --> 00:24:10,960
