551
00:24:20,480 --> 00:24:21,720
Let's wait for two more days.

552
00:24:28,280 --> 00:24:29,840
What evil plan are you up to now?

553
00:24:30,700 --> 00:24:31,800
I'm telling you,

554
00:24:32,200 --> 00:24:34,240
if you swindle me again

555
00:24:34,240 --> 00:24:35,320
like you did last time,

556
00:24:36,640 --> 00:24:37,800
