562
00:24:50,000 --> 00:24:51,520
If Sixth Sister won't agree,

563
00:24:51,520 --> 00:24:53,520
whatever plans are made will be in vain.

564
00:24:56,440 --> 00:24:57,960
The spring comes,

565
00:24:57,960 --> 00:24:59,360
It is a good timing.

566
00:25:00,120 --> 00:25:02,120
I'll go in front of Her Highness the Empress

567
00:25:02,120 --> 00:25:03,360
