568
00:25:03,360 --> 00:25:05,320
to organize a polo match for me.

569
00:25:05,600 --> 00:25:06,760
At that time,

570
00:25:06,760 --> 00:25:08,125
I will invite all the women

571
00:25:08,125 --> 00:25:09,360
of prestigious families,

572
00:25:09,880 --> 00:25:11,760
including your Sheng Family.

573
